title: JeeJaan® 6 Rolls Clear Mini Handy Shrink Wrap 100mm x 150m 17mu - Extended Core Self-Adhering Pallet Stretch Wrapper - Heavy Duty Plastic Wrap for Moving House Furniture Wrapping Film
features: ✅ STRONG WRAPPING FILM: JeeJaan offers 6 Rolls of clear mini handy wrap. This extended core stretch film is 100mm wide and 150m long with 17 microns thick cast film, perfect for wrapping, luggage, furniture, tools, and more. Made from strong material to prevent tears, it is ideal for small items, bags, and polythene roll needs.

✅ WATERPROOF AND MOISTURE PROOF: The mini pallet wrap roll adheres to itself, creating a sealed barrier that protects against dirt, dust, and moisture. Its strong stretch film prevents punctures or tears to the wrapped items.
✅ WRAP AND PROTECT: Our handheld pallet wrap has a handle that's just right for holding comfortably. The grip is made to be easy to use, so you can wrap things of any size without any trouble.

✅ VERSATILE APPLICATION: Handy stretch wrap serves multiple purposes, securing boxes, products, frames, and all sorts of small fragile items. It's a quicker alternative to strapping or taping, offering easy removal without leaving any sticky residue.

✅ CUSTOMER SATISFACTION WITH JEEJAAN: We meticulously design our stretch wrap rolls, focusing on quality and performance to meet customer expectations. Jeejaan’s stretch wrap provides reliable protection and ease of use, ensuring complete satisfaction. Perfect for pallet wrap, shrink wrap, and stretch film needs.
